{
  "info": {
    "name": "PlutusPM CRE SaaS - GraphQL (Fixed)",
    "description": "GraphQL-only collection for PlutusPM backend (PostGIS + RLS + 6 schemas). All queries use correct field names after fix 00016+00017 (extra_search_path + SELECT grants + introspection enabled). Use with anonKey + userJwt from Auth.\n\nHow to use:\n1. Import this collection + PlutusPM.postman_environment.json\n2. Set env: supabaseUrl=http://127.0.0.1:54321, anonKey from supabase status\n3. Run Auth > Sign Up / Sign In to auto-save userJwt + userId\n4. Run Introspection to see all available fields, then run domain queries\n\nField naming after fix: No schema prefix for unique tables (portfoliosCollection, sitesCollection, organizationsCollection, etc). If you still get Unknown field, run Introspection query to list actual names.\n\nBuilt after fixing: config.toml extra_search_path, geography type, nested $$, publication duplicate, d.portfolio_id, graphql introspection disabled, graphql_public owner error.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Auth (REST - Get JWT)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Sign Up - demo@cre.local",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (json.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userJwt', json.access_token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', json.user.id);",
                  "    console.log('JWT saved');",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "apikey", "value": "{{anonKey}}", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"demo@cre.local\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"data\": { \"full_name\": \"Demo Admin\" }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabaseUrl}}/auth/v1/signup",
              "host": ["{{supabaseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "signup"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Sign In - Get JWT",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userJwt', json.access_token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId', json.user.id);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', json.refresh_token);",
                  "  console.log('JWT saved, userId:', json.user.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "apikey", "value": "{{anonKey}}", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"demo@cre.local\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabaseUrl}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password",
              "host": ["{{supabaseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "token"],
              "query": [{ "key": "grant_type", "value": "password" }]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. GraphQL Introspection (Debug)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Introspection - List All Query Fields",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "apikey", "value": "{{anonKey}}", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{userJwt}}", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "graphql",
              "graphql": {
                "query": "query IntrospectFields {\n  __schema {\n    queryType {\n      fields {\n        name\n        description\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}",
                "variables": ""
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabaseUrl}}/graphql/v1",
              "host": ["{{supabaseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["graphql", "v1"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Introspection - List Mutation Fields",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "apikey", "value": "{{anonKey}}", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{userJwt}}", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "graphql",
              "graphql": {
                "query": "query IntrospectMutations {\n  __schema {\n    mutationType {\n      fields {\n        name\n        description\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}",
                "variables": ""
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabaseUrl}}/graphql/v1",
              "host": ["{{supabaseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["graphql", "v1"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Debug - Check Grants",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "apikey", "value": "{{anonKey}}", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{userJwt}}", "type": "text" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "graphql",
              "graphql": {
                "query": "query DebugGrants {\n  graphqlTablesDebugCollection {\n    edges {\n      node {\n        schemaName\n        tableName\n        anonCanSelect: anonSchemaUsage\n        authCanSelect: authSchemaUsage\n        anonSelect: anonSelect\n        authSelect: authSelect\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}",
                "variables": ""
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabaseUrl}}/graphql/v1",
              "host": ["{{supabaseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["graphql", "v1"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
